== Mentor Learning Path

Mentors play a critical role in helping podlings learn the Apache Way.  
This path introduces the core responsibilities and provides exercises to practice.

== Steps

1. **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Mentor+Quick+Start+Guide[Mentor Quick Start Guide]   
2. **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Onboarding[Mentor Onboarding]  
3. **Quiz:** link:https://canvas.instructure.com/enroll/JHL8BM[ASF Mentor Onboarding Quiz]  
4. **Practice:** link:https://canvas.instructure.com/enroll/GXPFY3[Mentor Scenarios Training]
5. **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Best+Practices+for+Mentors[Best Practices for Mentors] 
6. **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Case+Studies[Incubator Case Studies]
7. **Read:** link:- link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentors+Tough+Conversation+Guide[Mentors Tough Conversation Guide]

